Ngokuthola kwaleli phephandaba amaphoyisa ezwe ngesigameko sabalisa abebephanga amagaraji amabili emuva kokugamanxa kwehora lesibili entathakusa izolo. Kuthiwa abesilisa abebehlome ngezinhlokohlela zezibhamu batheleke emagaraji bafuna imali nogwayi bashaya bachitha. Kukholakala ukuthi baqale kwelinye igaraji bathatha imali engadalulwanga base bedlulela kwelinye bathatha ugwayi kuphela. Ngesikhathi amaphoyisa egasela endaweni yesehlo ahlangatshezwe yintululwane yezinhlamvu. Kulimale amaphoyisa amathathu aphuthunyiswe esibhedlela ngenxa yamanxeba okudutshulwa. Umthombo waleli phephandaba uthe abesilisa abebezimboze ubuso bagadle kuqala ngenhlamvu emaphoyiseni. Kusolakala ukuthi abasolwa abasagcwele amathafa babaleke ngezimoto eziyisithupha okubalwa kuzo amaBMW neMercedes Benz nezinye ezingazange ziqinisekiswe ukuthi ziwuhlobo luni. Okhulumela amaphoyisa kuzwelonke, uColonel Brenda Muridili, ukuqinisekisile ukuthi amaphoyisa asinde ngokulambisa ehlaselwa abalisa abebehlomile bezifihle ubuso. Uthe kulimale amaphoyisa amathathu aphuthunyiswa esibhedlela. Uqhube wathi elinye iphoyisa lidedeliwe esibhedlela kanti amabili asalulamela khona. “Amaphoyisa asephume umkhankaso wokuthungatha abasolwa abathinteka kulesi sigameko,” kusho uCol Muridili.